{
  "texts": [
    "Developed by Meta AI, it comes in various sizes spanning from 7 to 65 billion parameters.",
    "Utilizing an auto-regressive approach and built upon the transformer decoder architecture, Llama 2 takes sequences of text as input and predicts subsequent tokens through a sliding window mechanism for text generation.",
    "In our study, Llama 2 with 7 billion parameters was employed to assess the presence of fear in AI-related news headlines.",
    "The model's ability to understand context and nuance was leveraged without further fine-tuning.",
    "This approach stems from the model's extensive training on diverse text data, which provides a rich understanding of linguistic patterns and emotional expressions."
  ]
}